item.description:
Launch time: 11:30 a.m. from Pipers Cove at the Squam Lakes Association Estimated Return: 5:30 p.m. To launch site Estimated Distance: 12-14 miles This trip is open to sea kayaks 12 ft or longer. Shorter boats will not be able to keep the pace. I've invited paddlers from Champlain Kayak Club to join this paddle, that is why there are only 10 slots.

$5 launch fee, charts available for $5 Unload on the ramp, park in field above the Association building
